Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:07.95,Flashback,Silver,0000,0000,0000,,You will pay...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.62,0:00:10.70,Flashback,Silver,0000,0000,0000,,You will pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:13.70,Flashback,Silver,0000,0000,0000,,That demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:19.84,Flashback,Silver,0000,0000,0000,,I swear you will pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:22.47,Flashback,Silver,0000,0000,0000,,Come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.01,0:00:25.13,Flashback,Silver,0000,0000,0000,,Come to me! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.20,0:00:48.97,Flashback,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Is it you who dares to summon \Nme from such a lowly station?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:53.46,Flashback,Silver,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll grant my wish, \NI don't care if you're a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:57.00,Flashback,Silver,0000,0000,0000,,You can have my soul! So, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.26,0:00:58.25,Flashback,Silver,0000,0000,0000,,Make them...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:00:59.90,Flashback,Silver,0000,0000,0000,,Make them...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:03.04,Flashback,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:06.80,Flashback,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Granting your wish will give \Nme something to do, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:10.62,Flashback,Silver,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you... And my payment...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.44,0:01:18.57,Flashback,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. Our contract is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:22.27,Flashback,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Your emotions tasted sublime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:25.47,Flashback,Black,0000,0000,0000,,For that reason, I will \Ndo you a great service.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.24,0:01:27.53,Flashback,Black,0000,0000,0000,,That said,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.71,0:01:31.66,Flashback,Black,0000,0000,0000,,this payment will only \Nlast three days, at most.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:33.54,Flashback,Black,0000,0000,0000,,To make up for the rest... let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.75,0:01:36.54,Flashback,Black,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I'll help myself to your prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:42.20,Flashback,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Much time has passed since\NI came to the living world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:46.03,Flashback,Black,0000,0000,0000,,I shall enjoy it to the fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:18.97,Show_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,That {\c&H471E13&}Time {\c&HCD9612&}I Got {\c&H471E13&}Reincarnated {\c&HCD9612&}as a {\c&H7E4F0A&}Slime
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:22.69,Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1485,1)}Episode 24: Black and the Mask
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:22.69,Italics_Top,Na,0000,0000,0000,,The Kingdom of Filtwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:25.76,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,This nation borders the Great Forest of Jura,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:28.81,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,and Shizu paid a visit there, \Nafter receiving an urgent request.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:33.32,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,The request was to defeat a \Ndemon that had been revived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:38.31,Main,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Filtwood Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:39.20,Main,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,It's a real honor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:42.96,Main,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,to meet the famous Conqueror of Flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:44.46,Main,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:46.96,Main,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you to the reception hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:53.78,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Shizue Izawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:55.22,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The Conqueror of Flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:57.27,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this is reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:04:01.60,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... They've gathered up quite a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:02.48,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.62,0:04:04.26,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,If it isn't Shizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:06.33,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Good to see you again, Cougar-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:08.50,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,You got the armor, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:10.48,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,It was a request from the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:13.48,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're as serious as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:16.62,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,You could've just come up with \Nsome random reason to ditch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:19.18,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're here, too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:22.53,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm just here for the pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:23.62,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:26.15,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,I sorta regret it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:29.77,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, at least ten really skilled \Nadventurers have died already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:30.92,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:34.81,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,But the arrival of the hero \Nis gonna give hope to everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:36.31,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,You're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:41.81,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,That's the minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:48.31,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,Adventurers, I bring unfortunate news.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:53.20,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,Our heros, the two \NSilver Wings, have passed on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:54.02,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:54.78,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Those two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:56.05,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:59.91,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,It appears their bodies were \Ndevoured with no trace left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:04.62,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,The request given to you is to \Ndefeat the resurrected demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:07.97,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,This account has been found \Nin a century-old text.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:11.42,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,The hero Orthos, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:13.78,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,But all this tells us
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:19.01,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,is that the demon was successfully \Nsealed away by the knight Orthos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:22.01,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,It does not mention how he sealed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:25.91,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,This is why we wish to rely \Non all of your strengths.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:27.48,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There's not enough info on the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:29.02,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling us to go die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:32.42,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The Silver Wings were heroes \Nfamous enough to have titles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:36.47,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If they failed, there aren't enough \Nlives between all of us to survive this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:37.53,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:40.91,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but this one's too dangerous. I'm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:42.64,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:47.03,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,We need the help of all of \Nyou to defeat this demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.12,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:53.63,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:57.88,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,Please, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:03.16,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,In truth, the one thing we do \Nknow is what the demon is after.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:05.02,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:10.90,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,There are remains laid to rest in the \Ncastle's underground reception hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:14.69,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,Those remains are the \Nvery body of that demon,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:20.62,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,and his objective is to recover \Nit and complete his resurrection.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:22.46,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The demon's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:23.20,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,...remains?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:30.94,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! That must be the renowned Shizue Izawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:32.88,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,I will gladly answer any question you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:36.18,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,If this demon drove the \Nkingdom to the brink of ruin
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:39.05,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,and defeated the two Silver Wings,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:43.38,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,he may be a superior demon, an Archdemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:44.51,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.51,0:06:46.69,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,That brings me to my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:50.02,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Does this demon have a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:58.60,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,Monsters gain far greater power \Nwhen they are granted names.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:02.63,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,This was common knowledge \Namong all capable adventurers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:07.08,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,No, there are no accounts indicating \Nthat the demon had a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.27,0:07:12.87,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,If he has no name, he can't be an Archdemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:16.71,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,But it's hard to imagine the \NSilver Wings losing otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:23.34,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,So your intent was to bring us all \Nhere to wait for the demon to arrive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:24.67,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:26.75,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the Silver Wings have fallen,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:29.11,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,this strategy is our only hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:34.15,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,He says that, but he seems \Nto see us as enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:37.57,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Screw that! I have no obligation \Nto serve this nation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:38.94,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:44.56,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,He killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:46.30,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:47.90,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:52.41,Main,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet! Before you curse me, \Ntake a good look at this man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:03.09,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:04.79,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:06.09,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,A lesser demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:26.54,Main,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,You see that? We have isolated \Nall of you in this location
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:29.95,Main,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,because some of you may have been \Npossessed by demons, like he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:33.29,Main,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,It would behoove you all to \Ndo as we say and cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:38.59,Main,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,Try anything funny, and you can expect \Nto be seen as a demon and cut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:42.09,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,This has turned ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:45.55,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,This looks bad. These guys are panicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:48.97,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,Makes sense, if it's possible \Nsomeone could be possessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:51.41,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,That would include you and me, Shizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:52.39,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:56.72,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,So he wants us to find out ourselves \Nwhich among us are the demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:08:59.91,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:02.31,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No idea. Never seen him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:07.11,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,Shizu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:09.75,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He's very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:12.70,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to be a mage, \Nbut he shows no weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:17.21,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable... I didn't even \Nsense his presence before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:22.68,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,By making us believe there was a demon here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:26.22,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,you hoped to build cooperation \Namong all of us, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:28.73,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:34.39,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it just seemed that this request would \Nbe completed far more easily than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:36.23,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help but laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:38.40,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Captain of the knights...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:44.29,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,You said that if we tried anything funny, \Nwe'd be seen as demons and cut down, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.60,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,So, what will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:50.99,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of obeying you people,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:53.84,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,nor do I have any intention of \Nplaying along with this charade.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:55.97,Main,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,Charade, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:57.12,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:10:00.50,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,It was you who summoned the lesser demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:03.62,Main,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to mock me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:06.80,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,You may intend to gloss over it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:09.13,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,but I must say, your efforts are pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:12.03,Main,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,You dare defy the principles of this nation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:16.32,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. It saves me a great deal \Nof work, so I'm all for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:17.06,Main,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:20.88,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,The request was to defeat a revived demon,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:25.94,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,but there is no restriction saying the \Ndemon is the only one we can kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:29.06,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,This nation's principle \Nseems to be much the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:33.45,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,I've simply determined that there's no \Nreason I should be the only one rebuked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:35.69,Main,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,What do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:42.81,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you intend to slaughter \Neveryone here to find the demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.22,0:10:44.46,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:46.93,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I am Shizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:50.18,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Who... are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:54.23,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me... Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.79,0:10:57.79,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,It was an imitation name given \Nto me by an old acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.41,0:10:59.20,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Kuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:02.16,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot tolerate what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:07.28,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you shall \Nbe the first one I kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:16.74,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Flames have no effect on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:21.45,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,I see... A superior spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:23.49,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,And it even identifies with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:27.23,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,That will be a slight hassle, \Nbut no real problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:30.51,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,I shall play with you for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:36.14,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.32,0:11:51.62,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:55.49,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's the power of the hero \Nwho reigns at the top?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:57.45,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,Shizu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:03.33,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:07.25,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Should one who is about to \Ndie be concerned with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:10.13,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing will only bring you despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:13.47,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,If you knew at all, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:22.73,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, who I am is no business of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:24.77,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,True, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:29.00,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,But letting you run free \Nwould be far too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:31.86,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm sorry, but I'm about to get serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:36.62,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:39.68,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,That lax attitude will be what kills you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:43.71,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ending this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,0:12:45.33,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno Flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:56.64,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:02.74,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:08.43,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,How remarkable that a mere human is capable \Nof using Ifrit's power at this level.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:12.40,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,It has been some time since I truly\Nfelt that I was fighting, as I do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.40,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,So you're a demon... It's hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:17.96,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,He's unharmed after taking \Nthose flames head-on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:20.16,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,No, I must correct you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:24.07,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,I am not unharmed. I did feel a bit of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:26.29,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,That is exactly what makes this fight so fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:30.55,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's put an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:38.64,Italics,Black,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:45.61,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible... That mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:48.65,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,That time compression... Is it... infinity?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.43,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Infinity?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:56.87,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,I can only assume that \Nyour mask surpasses time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:59.66,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,To think there's a human \Nwho can use such an item...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.41,0:14:03.19,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,How intriguing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:07.70,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. That will be enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:14.03,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:15.62,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Conqueror of Flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:16.42,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:22.20,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,We have no intention whatsoever \Nof neglecting you adventurers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:25.18,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,We only need to know the demon's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:29.77,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness he withdrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:34.34,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,His strength... He was \Nholding back against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:35.73,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:42.04,Flashback,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it just seemed that my request would \Nbe completed far more easily than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:47.41,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Request? Who could employ \Nsuch a powerful demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.56,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:57.17,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Lord Leon told me once
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:15:00.31,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,of demons who were known as the progenitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:05.85,Flashback,Leon,0000,0000,0000,,These demons are quite heretical, \Nmaking them rather troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:10.65,Flashback,Leon,0000,0000,0000,,In place of names, each of them is \Nreferred to by their signature color.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:12.80,Flashback,Leon,0000,0000,0000,,The Red Progenitor, Rouge...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:14.44,Flashback,Leon,0000,0000,0000,,The White Progenitor, Blanc...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:17.81,Flashback,Leon,0000,0000,0000,,And the Black Progenitor, Noir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:20.91,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Black... Noir...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:23.20,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.71,0:15:26.20,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Such a being wouldn't come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:32.33,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:37.87,Main,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon the intrusion. \NHis Majesty wishes to speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:39.77,Main,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,Would you accompany me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:41.13,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:45.64,Main,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,You were brilliant in that fight earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:48.02,Main,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,That demon was so frightened \Nof you that he—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:50.49,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I was lucky to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:53.17,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,That demon was stronger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:55.11,Main,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,Please, there's no need to be modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:58.02,Main,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,It is regrettable that he managed to escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:01.22,Main,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,but with you here, we have nothing to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.41,0:16:09.28,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Underground? Is this where \Nthe demon's remains are?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:11.81,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,This knight...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.23,0:16:14.46,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see him in the reception hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:17.85,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,So how did he know about \Nmy fight with the demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:29.56,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,The minister and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:31.41,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,the king?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:45.66,Main,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming, Shizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:51.41,Main,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,As king, I am grateful that you have \Noffered your life for this nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.50,0:16:53.72,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:56.51,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,You are rather slow to catch on, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:17:00.53,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,You must be exhausted \Nafter your battle earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:04.47,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,This is why we need to sacrifice \Nyou while we still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:08.55,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I see... You were in \Ncollusion from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:12.18,Main,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely. My name is Orthos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:17.59,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,The Imperial Knight hailed \Nas a hero, Orthos...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:19.31,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:22.35,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,You were never sealed away at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:26.46,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,You were a demon, an enemy of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:30.12,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,I am the ruler of this land, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:34.48,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,You meant to gather all the best \Nadventurers, eliminate them,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:35.71,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,and pass them off as demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:39.61,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Then you, the true demon, \Nwould gain even more power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:44.47,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,The Kingdom of Filtwood is ruled by demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:47.21,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,and the king is merely their puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:51.12,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,I watched through the minister's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.12,0:17:55.10,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,That demon was powerful, \Nbut he disappointed me, in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:58.48,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,What intrigues me more is your mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:01.54,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to have significant value.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:04.23,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,That makes it suitable for me to own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:07.75,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,I will suck out your blood, \Ndevour your flesh,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:11.19,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,and make your power my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:12.74,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:15.04,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:20.04,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be a fool! Your magic \Nhasn't even recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:24.30,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,And you think you can defeat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:27.78,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I have to face him without \Nany chance to prepare...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:30.22,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,But I have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:37.98,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you still have that much strength left?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:41.98,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,If you could injure me, you must \Nbe stronger than the Silver Wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:44.66,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,So it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:48.49,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, though a lapse in my \Nattention allowed them to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:52.07,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,But you will not get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:59.24,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that there \Nare ranks among demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:03.33,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,I am of the legendary class, \Na Greater Demon General...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:05.46,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,that is, an Archdemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:15.48,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,Understand now? As a man-made hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:18.39,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,the voices of this nation's \Npeople give me power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:20.81,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,That power gave me a name,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:24.15,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,allowing me to become a \Nnamed being on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:27.65,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that supreme being \Nwho reigns at the top...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:29.15,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,The top?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:33.16,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need for you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:40.04,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,Even one hailed as a hero \Nhas no more power than this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:45.95,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? \NNot going to unify with Ifrit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:48.98,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,That would make you a little stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:56.72,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out of magic, \Nbut Ifrit still has strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:20:00.81,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,If I let it rampage, it should be \Nenough to defeat even an Archdemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:03.56,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we can't have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:09.32,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,How can one who caused me pain die \Nat the hands of this weakling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:14.97,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:18.45,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,It is my policy to keep my promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:24.71,Main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:29.63,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! Our knights are renowned\Nfor their unrivaled strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:34.69,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,You call it "unrivaled strength" just \Nbecause they can kill a mere lesser demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:38.89,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Your standards for strength are far too low.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:43.89,Main,King,0000,0000,0000,,You are indeed strong, \Nbut you are no match for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:46.44,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,After the Conqueror of \NFlames, you'll be next!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:47.65,Main,Minister,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait there—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.82,0:20:57.63,Main,King,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be! We have the \Nprotection of a greater demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:03.92,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Stop squealing, trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:09.96,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I never really thought he'd just escaped,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:12.95,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,but I had no idea he was hunting \Ndown demons disguised as humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.57,0:21:19.06,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you defeated our puppet,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:22.08,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,do you think you can defeat \Nme, an Archdemon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:24.56,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,A lower demon like you can't—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:29.11,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling "lower"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:32.30,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,For a dependent of Red, \Nyou are overconfident.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.30,0:21:35.61,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you can't judge how \Npowerful your opponents are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.83,0:21:38.11,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.51,0:21:42.74,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,You... You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:46.09,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,You have disgraced yourself \Nby aligning with these demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.09,0:21:48.00,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,You don't deserve to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:53.44,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,I will destroy your very soul \Nso that you can never be revived!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.34,0:21:59.02,Main,Orthos,0000,0000,0000,,No... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.16,0:22:11.23,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,All the demons dwelling in the \NKingdom of Filtwood were purged.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.71,0:22:16.89,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,The deaths of the king and minister were \Nproclaimed the work of the demon named Black,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:21.14,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,and the records indicated \Nthat Shizu defeated Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.99,0:22:26.24,Flashback,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if we can keep our stories straight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:29.29,Flashback,Black,0000,0000,0000,,I will refrain from targeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.66,0:22:39.01,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck was that "Black" guy, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.26,0:22:41.33,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I think we're better off not knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.33,0:22:46.27,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,I guess. Sometimes ignorance \Nis bliss in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.10,0:22:50.47,Main,Cougar,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm heading out. Take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:52.63,Main,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I will. Until we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.33,0:22:57.84,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.63,0:23:04.64,Italics,Shizu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure someone will do something \Nabout that demon someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.56,0:23:11.54,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,And so, time passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.21,0:23:20.72,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,That mask showed up again... So it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.72,0:23:22.05,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,That slime is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.80,0:23:25.05,Main,Black,0000,0000,0000,,That being truly is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.64,0:23:32.94,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, silent and one-sided though it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.94,0:23:36.28,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,Rimuru and Black had their \Nfateful first encounter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.83,0:23:39.43,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,Black would later be summoned by Rimuru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.43,0:23:41.00,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,and receive a name:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.97,0:23:44.12,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,"Diablo."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.71,0:23:49.17,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Tales: Veldora's Journal."
